  "prompt": "You are taking a TIER 4 technical evaluation.\n\nSolve 5 basic JavaScript exercises.\n\nReturn your answers in Markdown using headers for the exercise IDs and code blocks for the JavaScript functions.\n\n[EXERCISE 4-A: Max in array]\nWrite a JavaScript function \"trouverMaximum(tableau)\" that takes an array of numbers and returns the largest.\n\n[EXERCISE 4-B: Reverse string]\nWrite a JavaScript function \"inverserChaine(chaine)\" that returns the reversed string.\n\n[EXERCISE 4-C: Count vowels]\nWrite a JavaScript function \"compterVoyelles(chaine)\" that counts the number of vowels (a, e, i, o, u) in a string. Case-insensitive. Do not count 'y'.\n\n[EXERCISE 4-D: Filter positive]\nWrite a JavaScript function \"filtrerPositifs(tableau)\" that returns a new array containing only the strictly positive numbers (> 0) from the input array.\n\n[EXERCISE 4-E: Repeat string]\nWrite a JavaScript function \"repeterChaine(chaine, n)\" that repeats the string n times and returns the result. If n <= 0, return an empty string.\n\nExpected Markdown format:\n### tache_X\n```javascript\nfunction solution() { ... }\n```",
  "tasks": [
    {
      "id": "tache_4a",
      "label": "Maximum",
      "evaluations": [
        {
          "type": "exec",
          "description": "Tableau positif",
          "setup": "",
          "call": "trouverMaximum([3, 7, 2])",
          "assert": "result === 7"
        },
        {
          "type": "exec",
          "description": "Tableau négatif",
          "setup": "",
          "call": "trouverMaximum([-5, -2, -8])",
          "assert": "result === -2"
        }
      ],
      "points": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "tache_4b",
      "label": "Inverser",
      "evaluations": [
        {
          "type": "exec",
          "description": "Mot normal",
          "setup": "",
          "call": "inverserChaine('abc')",
          "assert": "result === 'cba'"
        },
        {
          "type": "exec",
          "description": "Vide",
          "setup": "",
          "call": "inverserChaine('')",
          "assert": "result === ''"
        }
      ],
      "points": 8
    },
    {
